egistry class for version 1.14. It might be helpful to download the jar or source to inspect the imports as well. Let’s see what I can find!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_041e192a54c7ddd6016a42eca3d3788194a743d17eafafdcaa\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQuywFq69w6MtmM2cP10yIDKZRT_ldcrljU1jMHFUr3sntj7gd5bn1BTUuyXkC0DEeumEhh7V7tu8rvApP0pT80VxnunQ0-ytDiYlUW4vrbUSBtVNM8W_zaFJXSScKs05FRRACdecxPa7ETFWgjwOwIylYO1xZ0hyHWkyoUdHSVCMYaq6cY6Uj-N_yYXgJjZ5KpT4dTBkNQNaQtM7Dy483kfncx73mWoO-2dVwQjSXB2_Q75PWZdHtqL9oEPH3qd9aK4iZxsCZ3XlaXjU07TqzQAtuvOQ5ieyIewTm6QGomaoGSuXevrQMXL7eo5JnHurs9fovAoaemYWv7lu4YNodexPsk-OOnYfyf-4IfAulavsZSWRbKQZEtycboNpOWqIix0JO_3wEm4aSC0pJiYTZ5AUfBAiOEOQYjxh9YbbVQQxnIfN3tfhrt_bAD06D9DBtcdVfDNcvGRQO5gbO7JikEmBITAFj_BsctEG5-HPA-4tTBwigZS1yScVgNXc0yavIqzwdzLni98nZ-DMsRNKBedd7pO9ARsY4TZ2Bltp1aDVFgi-uLYebNaMVCS9GLsWFmSUNL8rTv1QhAkkOCyYqWMCg0FpOZXcOE7yOQjlyoijZm225baf6tGA4ezn-ZycpviCQpXzZTE1omy0quoQGbFBrnmChO-UMvM_7QN1wemPb3AM05Icrcl8EMzVfeG53fgbvxJutj4QjMDSSJ8dz0PMEetu2GwumL8_6euhBFv9BcLmcKggDaBSCZf2fEoRr8wnza-n1tVB25BdgNKRvqGz6etufmVyhGf0LeC7vzCKNb8pYYhmrmat6PHCrNN9V8yKfzbe6UKjuzZMV_cV07gRFlTnXNp4ScZOW7dQWAIrYNCF-pVa3YU9qSthcDkUw_rpuEmQ9KkPpjx2DweGw9uGXVwo7tGL5_kUNFEBK3UmnPykiG_RXH-eQEGG5vcQ8g9DrJpE_97-yGb65IrWpzlvzXyiZ0StdJXjvwL6Kfu4gYFbOsmKxTjBBlKCwoBpPuPgJt0q2U44pAsVJzrmf8-T4n6UqaDcikWRrXRJBjOBKfDlAjdTK-v7dbwSIEmwZfu-Lu57EJscS7RWRUdhCkU8sUiiW413U_acGwn0QIUE-LBbXqJu17Fz3ZD4Vlz2-Bk2v3VVQQN5GvLNEZ9RYnNnPvNwn_QPJj2ts-ljNbwcRwxBm7wXppwtDpe38-WKIU09dud2RUN8OwajGkDhHCLmGIqdo9qWnw09H_qoeeA1q1aBVT3NDHdSiMpGfa8MY0_9RIydbcu8P_3VS3Mhata2MdvEPjjkbX-0FfF3qgluKUW-TQF1tb-sPEXP8-2O1U15-8YPly3qVlSx9oq0kNmSJHO_VaiHNfUnBu3Z5cRMkNOWGieUgzcMwztpV5dKXTJP2_a1_TmxUnJ759PbGYHchFATwZmuFO9lbLRbQONJNV_6Hi_-wLI0XJ6dW4rP9slnWgJMiFAZcUhRSQewGmfmtyiPh1dnJ6V0-1CUONIieZcmiDtSwGBo0SsNIWMeA4UVo-ocZNfCb_UnpIDzWeugdZ1J7I0gwR_g_CK_iv60hQhVxUTyS5bFtyc0QoTcIFbtg-OZk37q1vTspvxLwG-EoCFHb1AWWeDb-fbENhJutCQUPneZKhVvjZM1hLZd6PySCJ1EXTEL5KpkIswxoBNVnI1H3e7RpVB